object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM metal.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
		metal_acd.source_name, 
		metal_acd.load_type, 
		metal_acd.agency_nup, 
		metal_acd.contact_email, 
		metal_acd.contact_firstname, 
		metal_acd.contact_lastname, 
		metal_acd.contact_title, 
		metal_acd.created, 
		metal_acd.id,
		metal_acd.modified,
		current_batch.batch_id
FROM metal.adm_contact_guidewire metal_acd
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
    metal_acd.id,
    metal_acd.created,
    metal_acd.modified;

fields.expression:
MD5('source_name' || source_name || 'load_type' || load_type || 'o_contact_guidewire_datetime_created' || to_char(o_contact_guidewire_datetime_created) || 'o_contact_guidewire_datetime_modified' || to_char(o_contact_guidewire_datetime_modified) || 'o_agency_id' || to_char(o_agency_id) || 'contact_email' || contact_email || 'contact_firstname' || contact_firstname || 'contact_lastname' || contact_lastname || 'contact_title' || contact_title || 'o_agency_contact_guidewire_id' ||
to_char(o_agency_contact_guidewire_id))

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
        contact_guidewire_row_id, 
        contact_guidewire_row_md5checksum, 
        agency_contact_guidewire_id,  
  contact_guidewire_datetime_modified,
  contact_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime	
    FROM bronze.adm_contact_guidewire
    where  contact_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
